data.description:
Multiple offers: highest and best by noon on 11/22/21. Spacious home with plenty of upgrades located with easy access to IH35. Huge living room w/ over sized formal dining that opens up to the eat in kitchen - perfect for entertaining. (currently used as a game room w/ nego. pool table) Updated hardwood floors. All bedrooms upstairs. Over sized Master w/ room for desk or sitting area - en suite bath - Shower only. Large secondary rooms w/ walk-in closets. 2nd living room at upstairs landing would be great for the kids! Great backyard w/ covered back patio, storage room & mature trees. Water Softener owned. 
New Roof 7/2021 - Call today for your private tour. CISD
